The evidence with the title 'Trump in Japan: 'try building your cars in the U.S.' ' says Nov 6, 2017  ... President tells Japanese carmakers they need to build cars in the United States – even though many are built here .  ... And we love it when you build cars — if you ' re a Japanese firm , we love it — try building your cars in the United States instead of shipping them over . Is that possible to ask? That's not rude. 
